  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Rogue Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Debilitating Strike</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Iron Palm:</strong> Choose an additional Melee Weapon Style. When you make an Attack with an Unarmed Strike, you can use both Weapon Enhancements.</p><p><strong>Step of the Wind:</strong> You gain an additional +1 Speed and Jump Distance.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Roguish Finesse</span></strong></span></p><p>You gain 1 Skill Point.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Cheap Shot</span></strong></span></p><p>Cheap Shot now deals +2 damage instead.</p>",
